# Nutriflex Backend (NestJS)

This project is the **Nutriflex backend** (NestJS + TypeORM + PostgreSQL). When editing or creating code:

- **Architecture:** Controller → Service → Repo → Database. Controller forwards to service; service calls repo only; repo holds all DB logic (QueryBuilder, no raw SQL).
- **Responses:** Use unified format `{ status, messageEn, messageAr, data, meta? }`.
- **DTOs:** CreateDto, UpdateDto, PaginationDto, SearchDto; use class-validator and @ApiProperty.
- **Controllers:** Swagger on every endpoint; CRUD + GET /search + PUT /:id/toggle-status.
- **Code style:** TypeScript, camelCase variables, PascalCase classes, no unused imports.

For full module/entity/repo/DTO patterns and templates, follow **.cursor/instructions.md** and use **.cursor/templates/**.
